#	Technique / Concept	Use Explanation
1	File Handling	open(), os.path.exists(), json.load(), json.dump() for persistent storage
2	Dictionaries	To store customer, account, and transaction data (key-value structure)
3	Functions (Modular Coding)	Reusable blocks like save_all(), transact(), menu_handler()
4	Control Flow	if, else, while, try/except for logic handling
5	User Input Validation	Check for positive numbers, valid choices, existing usernames, etc.
6	String Formatting	Using f"..." to print messages and combine strings
7	CLI Menu System	Simple text-based interface for navigation
8	Authentication System	Admin and customer login with credential checks
9	ID Generation	Auto-generate customer account IDs dynamically
10	setdefault() Usage	Clean way to handle list initialization in a dictionary
11	Persistent Storage using JSON	Keeps all data in .txt files between program runs
